lead_paragraph: The Canadian Olympic Committee is hoping to tap into some of the country's Winter Games mojo by building a Rio de Janeiro Olympic brand campaign it hopes will leave people cold.

headline.print_headline: Canada Looks to Winter for Summer Olympics Mojo
